Package: murderParty
Type: Package
Title: Framework for Managing Interactive Murder Mystery Parties
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Jane", "Doe",
      email = "jane@example.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides a framework for running interactive murder mystery games. It includes functions for managing game state, player actions (such as searching for clues, interacting with objects or characters), and a Shiny-based web interface for players and game masters. Initially designed for the 'Habemus Papam' scenario, with potential for extension to other stories.
License: CC BY 4.0
Encoding: UTF-8
